snippet.title: Paladin's Oath Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for my game Paladin's Oath released on Steam in March 2022.

Wishlist / Download the game and free soundtrack on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1671590/Paladins_Oath/

Join the discussion for feedback and suggestions on Discord:
https://discord.gg/PqFpUJGc3T

Follow me on Twitter:
https://twitter.com/firebiscuitgame

Join the Reddit Game Community:
https://www.reddit.com/r/paladinsoath/

Lost? We also have a Wiki:
https://paladinsoath.fandom.com/wiki/Paladin%27s_Oath_Wiki

Fire Biscuit Games studio website for newsletter and upcoming games announcements:
https://games.firebiscuit.com
